Subject: Re: [VB] Berg Shifter?

I ran a short shift kit and a shift extension in my 66 westy, and it worked
great.  I heard someone say once that it doesn't work/cant be done, but it
worked fine for me.  A Berg shifter is nice, but overkill in a bus IMHO.

Eric
64 delux

